                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>012300</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp. <citedRange>164-167</citedRange> (content, date), p. <citedRange>303</citedRange>, number 44 (text)</bibl>.</p>
                    <p>Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#chevrollier2018-2019"/>, pp. <citedRange>79-80</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                        <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/> <citedRange>68.1742</citedRange></bibl>.
                        For a general bibliography on the accounts of the damiergoi see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011400</ref>.
